# Test Data Directory

Store test data and database backups here:

```
data/
├── 2024-11-17/
│   ├── test-db-backup.sql
│   ├── sample-surveys.json
│   ├── test-config.json
│   └── ...
├── 2024-11-18/
│   └── ...
```

## What to Store

- Database backups before/after testing
- Sample survey data used in tests
- Configuration files
- Log files
- IndexedDB exports
- Test user data

## Naming Convention

`[type]-[description]-[date].[ext]`

Examples:
- `test-db-backup-2024-11-17.sql`
- `sample-surveys-kish-grid-2024-11-17.json`
- `test-config-offline-mode-2024-11-17.json`
